          <li><strong>Uploaded Content:</strong> invoices (PDF), images you upload</li>
          <li><strong>Authentication Data:</strong> SMS verification codes</li>
          <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> device info, logs, crash reports, analytics</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

